com.emiliano.fmframework.core

Interface FeatureModel<SoftElement>

  • Type Parameters:
    SoftElement - the generic type
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FeatureModelImpl

    public interface FeatureModel<SoftElement>
    The Interface FeatureModel defines the basic operations for building a feature model and accessing its elements (features, tree and cross-tree constraints).
